  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "An animation is an effect, such as a fade-in, that’s applied to an individual component. Apple News Format has these animations for components:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsFormat/AppearAnimation",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Causes the component to appear.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsFormat/FadeInAnimation",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Causes the component to fade into view.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsFormat/MoveInAnimation",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Causes the component to move into view from the left or right side of the screen.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsFormat/ScaleFadeAnimation",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Causes the component to fade into view and scale up.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "An ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "animation",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " is different from a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "behavior",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": ". An animation occurs only once each time the user views the article, while a behavior is persistent and always in effect as long as the user is viewing the article. See ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/about-component-behaviors",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can apply a combination of animations and behaviors to a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "chapter",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "section",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " component by using a scene. See ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/adding-a-scene-to-a-chapter-or-a-section-header",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
